      <div class="article-top">
                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">Hunkering inside with Nextflix and a pile of takeout doesn&#039;t have to be a bad thing for your body. Choosing the right flick can reset your fitness goals and reinvigorate your commitment to healthy living.  </div>
